OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy morning with
OL,6,Fsome brighter intervals and the odd
OL,7,Fspot of rain possible. Remaining
OL,8,Flargely cloudy in the afternoon with
OL,9,Foutbreaks of mostly light rain
OL,10,Fspreading eastwards. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be a cloudy evening
OL,13,Fwith light and patchy rain easing. Dry
OL,14,Ffor a time, but further rain will soon
OL,15,Fspread eastwards overnight, mostly
OL,16,Faffecting northern areas.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,19,Foutbreaks of light and patchy rain.
OL,20,FSome brief brighter spells at times,
OL,21,Fespecially in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
